## Documentation
  - https://mallinson.ca/posts/5/the-perfect-web-development-environment-for-your-new-mac
  - https://jasonmccreary.me/articles/install-apache-php-mysql-mac-os-x/

## 1. Installations

  * Install xcode tools (necessary only for the command line's tools)
      - xcode-select --install
  
  * Install Brew (Mac OS package manager):
      - /usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"
    
    if it's already installed proced to update it:
      - brew update
